prodNameC: 常盈腎激素免疫放射分析組
ingredientsDesc:
A. Renin Standards: Five vials, labeled A-E, containing approximate concentrations of 0, 5, 20, 100, and 500 pg/ml of Renin (Active form) in serum.
B. Anti-Renin-Coated Beads: One bottle, containing 100 hundred beads coated with anti-human Renin antibody.
C. Anti-Renin [I-125] Reagent: One vial, 11 ml, containing < 10 μCi (370 kBq) of [I-125]-labeled anti-human Renin antibody in a protein-stabilized (BSA) buffer.
D. Renin Controls: Two vials containing low and high concentrations of human Renin in serum.
applicantName: 常盈實業股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市北投區永興路一段49號
efficacy: DSL-25100 ACTIVETM Renin放射免疫分析組可提供人體血清或血漿中Renin的定量測定。
